WEBVTT

01:43.020 --> 01:45.990
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.110 --> 01:49.110
[Episode 19]

02:24.470 --> 02:25.130
Qin Yue.

02:26.590 --> 02:27.750
Request for

02:28.430 --> 02:29.340
an arrest warrant.

02:30.240 --> 02:32.040
Monitor all surrounding transportation hubs,

02:32.100 --> 02:33.350
express railway stations,

02:33.430 --> 02:34.470
and train stations

02:34.530 --> 02:35.579
for traces of them.

02:45.800 --> 02:46.770
Keep watch here.

02:46.800 --> 02:47.800
I'll return to the station.

02:48.360 --> 02:49.090
Go on.

03:00.270 --> 03:01.810
[Police Inspection]

03:03.280 --> 03:04.200
Attention, guys.

03:04.220 --> 03:05.830
We can't rule out that

03:05.830 --> 03:06.510
the suspect

03:06.510 --> 03:07.320
is armed.

03:07.350 --> 03:08.740
Stay alert and be careful.

03:11.010 --> 03:11.650
Hello.

03:11.140 --> 03:12.410
[Police Inspection]

03:11.760 --> 03:12.530
Routine check.

03:21.320 --> 03:23.870
[Public Security]

03:23.960 --> 03:25.240
[Police]

03:25.320 --> 03:28.310
[Ninghai High-Tech Zone]

03:28.400 --> 03:30.140
[Tollgate]

03:37.850 --> 03:41.060
[Ninghai High-Tech Zone]

03:41.300 --> 03:42.390
Jiang Chengyi.

03:42.790 --> 03:44.420
What kind of captain are you?

03:44.840 --> 03:46.060
Two deaths

03:46.120 --> 03:47.380
and a cop injured?

03:47.670 --> 03:49.110
You found zero leads.

03:49.829 --> 03:50.790
In broad daylight,

03:50.840 --> 03:52.220
you even let them escape!

03:55.950 --> 03:56.760
Director.

03:57.240 --> 03:58.480
I was the first to arrive.

03:58.520 --> 03:59.230
It’s my fault.

03:59.380 --> 04:01.430
Captain Jiang was called to the scene last minute.

04:01.630 --> 04:02.920
Besides, this murderer

04:02.950 --> 04:03.840
is great at covering their tracks—

04:03.870 --> 04:05.110
I don't care who they are!

04:05.830 --> 04:06.960
Ninghai isn't a place where

04:06.990 --> 04:08.230
criminals can get off scot free!

04:10.590 --> 04:11.890
Set up a special investigation team now.

04:12.230 --> 04:13.190
From now on,

04:13.310 --> 04:14.290
I’ll supervise it myself!

04:16.070 --> 04:16.910
Jiang Chengyi.

04:18.029 --> 04:19.519
You have seven days.

04:20.029 --> 04:21.420
No matter what you do,

04:21.970 --> 04:23.570
you must arrest them!

04:23.990 --> 04:24.540
Yes!

04:26.340 --> 04:26.830
Yes.

04:36.780 --> 04:38.470
Based on the inspection

04:38.470 --> 04:39.650
of the scene,

04:39.790 --> 04:41.470
there are many bruises on Ding Jing's body

04:41.550 --> 04:43.630
and strangulation marks on her wrists and neck.

04:43.860 --> 04:46.430
There are obvious traces of her

04:46.510 --> 04:48.580
being assaulted or abused.

04:48.750 --> 04:50.180
The cause of death was strangulation.

04:52.750 --> 04:54.310
Any leads from Forensics?

04:54.430 --> 04:55.270
They said

04:55.310 --> 04:56.440
the victim's stomach was empty.

04:56.470 --> 04:57.440
She was probably

04:57.470 --> 04:58.730
starved for days.

05:00.200 --> 05:02.070
Based on Liu Hao’s description,

05:01.620 --> 05:03.380
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

05:02.110 --> 05:03.290
we've initially determined

05:03.430 --> 05:05.230
that this murderer is also the person

05:05.250 --> 05:06.150
who killed Wang Qianqian.

05:08.630 --> 05:10.150
This serial murderer

05:11.480 --> 05:13.120
is extremely arrogant

05:13.270 --> 05:14.830
and great at

05:14.910 --> 05:15.870
covering their tracks.

05:16.400 --> 05:17.940
They're also highly skilled

05:17.990 --> 05:18.800
in close combat.

05:19.180 --> 05:20.630
Everyone must stay alert.

05:20.880 --> 05:22.460
While you're being cautious,

05:22.710 --> 05:24.200
you also have to be meticulous.

05:24.350 --> 05:25.640
Don't miss a single trace

05:25.670 --> 05:26.550
of possible leads

05:26.580 --> 05:28.100
in this case.

05:28.590 --> 05:29.260
Qin Yue.

05:29.950 --> 05:31.490
Station people all over

05:31.750 --> 05:32.750
to keep the murderer

05:32.750 --> 05:33.620
within this city.

05:33.560 --> 05:36.540
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

05:36.980 --> 05:37.870
Lei Yiming.

05:38.070 --> 05:38.930
I have a task for you.

05:40.430 --> 05:41.790
Investigate Ding Jing's

05:41.830 --> 05:42.650
social relationships

05:42.680 --> 05:44.040
for any

05:45.140 --> 05:46.490
useful info and lead.

05:46.760 --> 05:47.340
Got it.

05:49.490 --> 05:50.440
You're all here.

05:50.710 --> 05:51.470
Why are you here?

05:52.360 --> 05:54.010
Director Xing sent me to help you.

05:54.260 --> 05:54.710
What?

05:54.960 --> 05:55.820
You don't welcome me?

05:56.030 --> 05:56.740
Of course I do.

05:56.770 --> 05:57.480
That's great.

05:58.280 --> 05:59.520
Is there any material I can read?

05:59.550 --> 06:00.320
Professor Yu.

06:06.940 --> 06:07.520
Hello?

06:13.350 --> 06:14.130
You're here.

06:17.880 --> 06:18.550
Brought me food?

06:21.520 --> 06:22.730
Are you going back later?

06:24.280 --> 06:25.280
I made use

06:25.310 --> 06:26.430
of my break

06:26.450 --> 06:27.340
to visit you.

06:28.160 --> 06:28.820
Right.

06:28.850 --> 06:30.390
I even saw Liu Hao.

06:30.520 --> 06:31.740
He insisted on being discharged.

06:33.150 --> 06:34.150
With his stab wound,

06:34.170 --> 06:35.310
can he be discharged so soon?

06:35.310 --> 06:36.350
No.

06:36.370 --> 06:38.260
So we need to observe him longer.

06:38.290 --> 06:39.370
Let him rest.

06:45.390 --> 06:46.150
What's wrong?

06:49.110 --> 06:50.670
A-Are you hurt?

06:51.990 --> 06:52.630
Me?

06:53.000 --> 06:53.770
I'm fine.

06:53.970 --> 06:54.960
Look, I'm in one piece.

06:58.340 --> 07:00.670
Did you come today

07:00.690 --> 07:02.010
to see if I'm hurt?

07:03.020 --> 07:04.440
I'm worried about you.

07:05.160 --> 07:06.290
You even know how to dote on others now.

07:13.030 --> 07:14.880
Will you be going home tonight?

07:16.410 --> 07:17.360
I think so.

07:17.700 --> 07:18.450
Miss me?

07:21.070 --> 07:21.910
Yeah, I miss you.

07:23.860 --> 07:24.860
I miss you too.

07:27.600 --> 07:29.130
I'll wait for you at home tonight.

07:29.150 --> 07:29.870
Sure.

07:30.280 --> 07:32.380
I might be a bit late.

07:35.670 --> 07:36.860
I can't eat with you.

07:36.950 --> 07:38.050
I have to go back.

07:38.070 --> 07:38.850
So soon?

07:39.030 --> 07:39.770
Take this back.

07:39.790 --> 07:40.630
I didn't eat much.

07:40.650 --> 07:41.270
Okay.

07:42.740 --> 07:44.010
I'll wait for you at home.

07:46.909 --> 07:48.290
Be careful on the road.

07:50.890 --> 07:52.460
Be careful.

07:54.670 --> 07:55.650
What was that for?

07:55.750 --> 07:56.590
Don't I say that

07:56.620 --> 07:57.350
to you guys too?

07:57.370 --> 07:58.030
I say that

07:58.050 --> 07:59.020
for every mission.

08:00.720 --> 08:02.210
How is it? Is it good?

08:03.160 --> 08:03.880
Not bad.

08:05.190 --> 08:06.370
Finish it quickly.

08:06.470 --> 08:07.390
There's still a lot of info

08:07.430 --> 08:08.070
for you to read.

08:08.390 --> 08:08.990
Okay, right away.

08:09.070 --> 08:09.780
I'll be right there.

08:09.850 --> 08:12.630
[Boya Porcelain] [Abandoned factory]

08:12.630 --> 08:15.060
[Ninghai City Map] [Jiang Chengyi: Criminal Police] [Take note]

08:15.060 --> 08:19.410
[Lu Yan: Anesthesiologist at Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

08:15.060 --> 08:19.410
[Jiang Chengyi: Criminal Police] [Take note]

09:03.140 --> 09:07.430
[Li Ruonan]

09:06.860 --> 09:08.130
Did you get it?

09:07.430 --> 09:09.810
[Mysterious Person]

09:11.740 --> 09:12.380
Sorry.

09:13.520 --> 09:14.240
Where is she?

09:22.900 --> 09:24.020
I made a mistake.

09:27.510 --> 09:28.370
I'm sorry.

09:28.830 --> 09:30.250
I'll make it up to you.

09:38.610 --> 09:40.570
This is what you should do.

09:42.840 --> 09:44.220
Can I see her?

09:45.550 --> 09:46.910
We'll talk after you get it.

09:47.530 --> 09:48.340
Remember,

09:48.400 --> 09:50.170
you have no second chances.

09:52.830 --> 09:53.820
I understand.

10:05.790 --> 10:06.830
So

10:06.870 --> 10:08.310
it's the same murderer?

10:11.600 --> 10:13.200
That's strange.

10:13.450 --> 10:15.560
According to the subway station footage,

10:15.590 --> 10:16.990
after Ding Jing left the station,

10:17.030 --> 10:18.230
she walked into the alley

10:18.350 --> 10:20.570
and then went to Jifu Village.

10:20.670 --> 10:21.510
This proves that

10:21.590 --> 10:22.950
Ding Jing knows the murderer.

10:24.030 --> 10:24.710
But after arriving

10:24.710 --> 10:26.560
at Jifu Village,

10:26.590 --> 10:28.710
why did the murderer detain Ding Jing

10:28.750 --> 10:30.080
and abuse and torture her?

10:30.680 --> 10:32.690
It seems like an interrogation.

10:33.880 --> 10:36.110
What could the murderer want to know

10:36.800 --> 10:37.940
from Ding Jing?

10:39.400 --> 10:40.970
Is there a possibility

10:41.120 --> 10:42.500
that it wasn't an interrogation?

10:43.030 --> 10:43.830
Maybe

10:43.860 --> 10:45.070
they just

10:45.100 --> 10:46.400
wanted to torture her?

10:46.430 --> 10:47.980
That's the other problem:

10:48.600 --> 10:50.280
the way Ding Jing was killed.

10:50.840 --> 10:52.580
Let's say it's the same murderer.

10:52.820 --> 10:53.870
Then they chose to kill the two

10:53.910 --> 10:55.590
by extremely different methods.

10:56.320 --> 10:57.560
In Wang Qianqian's case,

10:57.590 --> 10:59.040
you can clearly sense that

10:59.060 --> 11:01.100
the murderer's calm and professional.

11:01.130 --> 11:02.470
They didn't leave any trace.

11:02.520 --> 11:04.110
But with Ding Jing,

11:04.140 --> 11:05.730
they chose to strangle her.

11:06.910 --> 11:08.150
I'm leaning towards

11:08.170 --> 11:10.040
them killing Ding Jing on impulse.

11:10.060 --> 11:10.850
Exactly.

11:11.280 --> 11:12.120
We so happened

11:12.150 --> 11:13.890
to rush there in time,

11:13.920 --> 11:15.150
and they killed her

11:15.190 --> 11:16.120
to prevent being exposed.

11:16.220 --> 11:17.230
Isn't it logical?

11:18.900 --> 11:21.530
If they just wanted to kill someone,

11:22.110 --> 11:23.150
why did they torture

11:23.150 --> 11:24.430
and abuse her?

11:28.910 --> 11:29.750
A criminal

11:29.790 --> 11:31.350
this meticulous

11:31.670 --> 11:32.950
wouldn't be so hasty

11:32.970 --> 11:34.610
all of a sudden.

11:37.740 --> 11:38.600
So the key

11:38.600 --> 11:39.970
lies in whether

11:40.080 --> 11:41.840
the murderer got

11:41.870 --> 11:43.270
what they wanted.

11:44.480 --> 11:45.820
If they got it,

11:45.840 --> 11:47.060
they've accomplished their goal.

11:47.230 --> 11:48.590
If they didn't...

11:49.680 --> 11:51.590
They'll appear again.

11:53.070 --> 11:53.710
Right?

11:54.700 --> 11:55.480
Yes.

11:55.990 --> 11:57.030
From now on,

11:57.390 --> 11:59.020
let's focus on

11:59.050 --> 12:01.010
Ding Jing's residential area

12:01.320 --> 12:02.880
and the places she frequented.

12:03.230 --> 12:04.580
Let's see if this murderer

12:04.670 --> 12:06.510
will appear again.

12:07.900 --> 12:09.150
Come on, get to work.

12:09.600 --> 12:10.590
Let's split up.

12:28.370 --> 12:32.360
[B1 Parking Lot]

12:32.530 --> 12:33.370
What are you doing?

12:34.940 --> 12:36.110
-Stop!
-Stop!

12:37.480 --> 12:38.180
Stop!

12:37.870 --> 12:41.240
[B1 Parking Lot]

12:38.710 --> 12:39.230
Stop!

12:45.300 --> 12:46.790
That's all. Nothing else.

12:47.910 --> 12:48.590
Hey.

12:48.820 --> 12:49.590
Thanks for your help.

12:50.070 --> 12:50.540
Thank you.

12:50.560 --> 12:51.210
Did they call the police?

12:51.230 --> 12:51.810
Yes.

12:51.830 --> 12:52.560
What happened?

12:53.240 --> 12:54.340
Just now,

12:54.370 --> 12:55.230
someone

12:55.250 --> 12:56.580
broke the window

12:56.600 --> 12:57.420
of this car.

12:57.550 --> 12:58.230
We rushed here

12:58.230 --> 12:59.020
once we heard it.

12:59.390 --> 13:00.360
Did you see how they looked

13:00.360 --> 13:01.200
clearly?

13:01.470 --> 13:02.400
No.

13:02.440 --> 13:03.670
They were wearing a cap and a mask.

13:03.720 --> 13:04.610
I couldn't see their face.

13:04.640 --> 13:05.250
Right!

13:05.710 --> 13:07.600
And they ran too fast.

13:07.670 --> 13:09.360
We couldn't catch up with them.

13:10.190 --> 13:11.190
Okay, thank you.

13:11.210 --> 13:11.770
Thank you.

13:20.900 --> 13:21.430
How about this?

13:21.470 --> 13:22.410
Um, Yiming.

13:22.520 --> 13:23.270
Go get all

13:23.270 --> 13:24.300
the surveillance footage here.

13:24.320 --> 13:24.680
Okay.

13:24.710 --> 13:25.140
Sihan.

13:25.170 --> 13:26.320
Interview around to see

13:26.390 --> 13:27.270
if any drivers who

13:27.310 --> 13:28.150
entered the basement

13:28.150 --> 13:28.840
in this time period

13:28.910 --> 13:29.690
witnessed it.

13:29.830 --> 13:30.120
Okay.

13:30.150 --> 13:30.470
Okay?

13:30.510 --> 13:31.030
Let's work hard.

13:31.030 --> 13:31.910
See you in the team later.

13:31.990 --> 13:32.950
I’m leaving. Bye.

13:33.390 --> 13:34.110
Bye, guys.

13:34.200 --> 13:34.630
Thank you.

13:34.670 --> 13:35.200
Okay.

13:35.090 --> 13:37.930
[Anshan, Ninghai Public Security
Criminal Investigation Unit]

13:38.100 --> 13:39.400
Actually,

13:39.920 --> 13:41.800
there's something I don't understand.

13:42.550 --> 13:43.470
I know.

13:43.900 --> 13:44.960
The murder motive,

13:44.990 --> 13:45.550
right?

13:46.110 --> 13:46.750
Yes.

13:47.110 --> 13:48.320
If

13:48.740 --> 13:50.520
killing Wang Qianqian

13:50.810 --> 13:52.640
was to target Lu Yan,

13:53.000 --> 13:54.480
then why did they kill Ding Jing?

13:54.920 --> 13:55.590
Also,

13:55.620 --> 13:56.790
Ding Jing and Lu Yan

13:56.810 --> 13:57.770
actually

13:58.220 --> 13:59.810
aren't on good terms.

14:00.480 --> 14:02.710
What's the point of killing Ding Jing?

14:04.430 --> 14:05.910
Could it be that

14:06.420 --> 14:08.610
they're not only targeting Lu Yan?

14:08.930 --> 14:09.910
Then who's their target?

14:13.610 --> 14:14.230
Me?

14:15.140 --> 14:16.180
Think about it.

14:16.200 --> 14:18.220
The murderer disguising as Deng Man

14:18.250 --> 14:19.900
only happened after you came back.

14:20.550 --> 14:22.310
In the past eight years,

14:22.470 --> 14:23.600
nothing odd happened

14:23.630 --> 14:24.470
around you

14:24.490 --> 14:25.970
and Lu Yan.

14:26.430 --> 14:27.540
Why is that?

14:31.270 --> 14:34.170
Targeting the both of us?

14:34.710 --> 14:36.360
It's entirely possible.

14:36.670 --> 14:39.180
But as for the reason,

14:39.200 --> 14:40.700
I haven't figured it out yet.

14:43.770 --> 14:44.570
Jiang!

14:44.700 --> 14:45.310
Professor Yu.

14:45.350 --> 14:46.110
How is it?

14:46.940 --> 14:48.370
We found leads

14:48.410 --> 14:50.090
in an underground garage.

14:50.650 --> 14:52.710
They broke Ding Jing's car window.

14:53.810 --> 14:54.760
You're right.

14:54.780 --> 14:55.710
It seems that they're

14:55.710 --> 14:56.550
looking for something.

15:02.270 --> 15:03.440
From now on,

15:04.680 --> 15:05.950
at all the places

15:05.970 --> 15:07.640
Ding Jing used to be at,

15:07.760 --> 15:10.000
be it her home, her office,

15:10.020 --> 15:11.650
or anywhere she frequented,

15:12.570 --> 15:14.250
send people to keep watch

15:14.280 --> 15:15.270
in pairs.

15:16.120 --> 15:17.060
One more thing.

15:18.150 --> 15:19.740
We must figure out

15:19.760 --> 15:22.040
what the murderer is looking for.

15:22.510 --> 15:23.180
It's very important.

15:23.210 --> 15:23.880
Yes.

15:23.290 --> 15:26.840
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

15:32.620 --> 15:35.260
[Huiting Complex]

16:31.540 --> 16:32.520
You're back.

16:34.130 --> 16:35.220
Are you cold?

16:36.150 --> 16:37.250
I made something for you.

16:37.290 --> 16:38.290
Here. Come in.

16:45.940 --> 16:46.990
Are you

16:47.190 --> 16:47.790
tired?

16:57.740 --> 16:58.560
Lu Yan.

17:02.700 --> 17:04.410
I have something to tell you.

17:08.970 --> 17:10.089
Ding Jing is dead.

17:12.750 --> 17:13.869
She was killed.

17:19.200 --> 17:20.849
It's true that

17:21.200 --> 17:23.490
I hate Ding Jing because of Deng Man.

17:23.520 --> 17:24.079
But...

17:25.280 --> 17:27.089
I didn't expect her...

17:28.880 --> 17:30.530
to be killed.

17:32.000 --> 17:33.600
No matter how wrong she was,

17:33.630 --> 17:34.950
it shouldn't be like this.

17:37.840 --> 17:38.440
Lu Yan.

17:40.380 --> 17:41.480
Don't think too much.

17:42.550 --> 17:44.210
We will find the murderer.

17:52.340 --> 17:53.300
You must be tired.

17:53.570 --> 17:55.150
I'll heat up the dumplings for you.

17:55.390 --> 17:55.920
Okay.

19:48.920 --> 19:50.010
Jiang Chengyi.

19:50.260 --> 19:52.110
You will catch the murderer.

19:52.360 --> 19:53.070
You will.

20:06.220 --> 20:09.410
[Anshan, Ninghai Public Security
Criminal Investigation Unit]

20:12.950 --> 20:13.510
You're back.

20:13.530 --> 20:14.310
Are you busy?

20:17.550 --> 20:18.180
Jiang.

20:18.570 --> 20:20.400
I just came back from Ding Jing's place.

20:20.750 --> 20:21.870
I searched everywhere.

20:21.890 --> 20:23.610
There weren't any valuable leads.

20:23.640 --> 20:24.350
Some of our men are

20:24.370 --> 20:25.080
keeping watch there.

20:25.230 --> 20:26.550
But so far,

20:26.590 --> 20:27.790
no one suspicious has been found.

20:27.810 --> 20:29.040
But I checked a few parcels

20:29.070 --> 20:30.110
she's received recently

20:30.110 --> 20:31.860
and there was no sender.

20:32.040 --> 20:33.190
I'm unsure about it,

20:33.230 --> 20:33.600
so

20:33.630 --> 20:34.910
I brought it to you.

20:34.930 --> 20:35.680
What is it?

20:40.150 --> 20:41.620
This is interesting.

20:42.440 --> 20:44.090
When we were in university,

20:44.150 --> 20:44.670
this hairpin

20:44.670 --> 20:45.430
was popular

20:45.470 --> 20:46.380
among girls.

20:46.410 --> 20:47.970
Why did Ding Jing buy this?

20:48.360 --> 20:49.710
This doesn't go with the clothes

20:49.750 --> 20:50.390
she usually wore.

20:50.450 --> 20:51.110
Let me see.

20:51.110 --> 20:51.590
Is it hers?

20:52.080 --> 20:53.430
I don't know if it's hers.

20:53.450 --> 20:54.070
But it's

20:54.110 --> 20:55.070
a recent parcel she got.

21:15.560 --> 21:17.250
It should be a coincidence.

21:26.150 --> 21:29.610
[A small memorial service is scheduled to be held at 10:30 a.m. on January 7.]

21:26.150 --> 21:29.610
[My daughter, Ding Jing, has passed away recently.]

21:30.760 --> 21:32.510
Ding Jing's memorial service

21:32.940 --> 21:33.760
is this Saturday.

21:34.060 --> 21:35.280
Let's go together.

21:36.030 --> 21:38.340
The funeral is the best place to investigate

21:38.370 --> 21:39.850
a person's social relationships.

21:41.670 --> 21:43.520
Maybe the murderer will be there too.

21:46.090 --> 21:47.330
I have to go.

21:55.360 --> 21:56.660
Don't be nervous.

21:56.780 --> 21:58.850
It's just a first meeting today.

21:58.870 --> 21:59.750
They're not

21:59.790 --> 22:00.990
deciding on the role yet.

22:01.350 --> 22:03.190
But first impressions are too important.

22:04.150 --> 22:05.070
I feel like if

22:05.070 --> 22:06.370
I don't perform well today,

22:06.710 --> 22:08.070
there will be no next chance.

22:09.630 --> 22:10.440
Haven't you been

22:10.470 --> 22:12.110
taking Professor Yu's classes?

22:13.540 --> 22:14.590
I think I've learned

22:14.590 --> 22:15.750
enough from her.

22:17.230 --> 22:18.120
Did you quarrel?

22:19.350 --> 22:20.260
No.

22:20.650 --> 22:21.990
It's just a work partnership.

22:22.030 --> 22:23.240
We're not that close.

22:24.430 --> 22:25.240
You have to

22:25.270 --> 22:26.230
seize this opportunity

22:26.310 --> 22:28.100
and learn from Professor Yu.

22:28.240 --> 22:29.550
It'll also come in handy

22:29.550 --> 22:30.190
for future roles.

22:32.370 --> 22:33.750
But she's never been sincere

22:33.790 --> 22:34.790
in teaching me.

22:37.820 --> 22:38.330
Come in.

22:41.180 --> 22:42.010
Mr. Wen.

22:42.040 --> 22:42.870
This morning,

22:42.910 --> 22:43.870
we received a letter.

22:47.880 --> 22:52.790
[A small memorial service is scheduled to be held at 10:30 a.m. on January 7.]

22:47.880 --> 22:52.790
[My daughter, Ding Jing, has passed away recently.]

22:47.880 --> 22:52.790
[Obituary]

22:53.390 --> 22:54.310
Ding Jing passed away.

22:56.500 --> 22:57.320
No way.

22:57.350 --> 22:58.230
Didn't we just meet her

22:58.270 --> 22:59.270
at the mixer a few days ago?

23:01.630 --> 23:02.750
I'll be on a business trip.

23:03.340 --> 23:04.280
Send her off for me.

23:11.740 --> 23:12.350
Okay.

23:45.700 --> 23:46.270
Hello?

23:46.830 --> 23:48.060
What do you mean?

23:49.080 --> 23:50.310
I've searched Ding Jing's home

23:50.310 --> 23:51.470
and company.

23:51.800 --> 23:53.250
I didn't find anything.

23:54.060 --> 23:54.750
Could it be that

23:54.750 --> 23:55.870
she doesn't have evidence?

23:56.060 --> 23:57.090
Can you guarantee that?

23:59.070 --> 23:59.830
I'm sorry.

24:00.820 --> 24:03.020
If you still want to see your mother,

24:03.390 --> 24:04.470
you know what to do.

24:04.490 --> 24:05.400
Don't worry.

24:06.880 --> 24:07.980
I will find it.

24:54.430 --> 24:55.120
Yue.

24:55.200 --> 24:55.800
How is it?

24:56.560 --> 24:57.510
Nothing unusual.

24:57.720 --> 24:58.860
Go back and rest.

24:59.380 --> 25:00.740
It's okay. We're not sleepy.

25:00.770 --> 25:02.080
Just go back and rest.

25:02.110 --> 25:03.200
Or you can go to the hospital

25:03.220 --> 25:04.260
to accompany Liu Hao.

25:05.210 --> 25:05.850
Okay.

25:07.590 --> 25:08.310
Thank you, Yue.

25:08.310 --> 25:08.910
Where's the walkie-talkie?

25:09.050 --> 25:09.770
At the handle.

25:09.790 --> 25:10.400
Go.

25:10.670 --> 25:11.120
Bye.

25:11.270 --> 25:11.750
Take care.

25:11.750 --> 25:12.370
Be careful.

25:29.280 --> 25:30.090
Go in.

25:30.440 --> 25:31.930
Her parents are inside.

25:38.730 --> 25:39.970
My condolences, Mr. and Mrs. Ding.

25:42.360 --> 25:45.950
[Ms. Ding Jing's memorial service]

25:45.970 --> 25:49.890
[Ms. Ding Jing's memorial service]

25:45.970 --> 25:49.890
[May the imminent cold dissipate, and may heaven be a magnificent bed of roses]

26:04.690 --> 26:05.380
This way.

26:10.340 --> 26:11.850
My condolences, Mr. and Mrs. Ding.

26:14.930 --> 26:15.830
My condolences.

26:16.150 --> 26:16.740
Thank you.

26:18.360 --> 26:19.200
My condolences.

26:22.170 --> 26:23.330
My condolences.

27:08.770 --> 27:10.150
Qin Yue, how's it going there?

27:11.090 --> 27:12.450
Everything's normal.

27:13.350 --> 27:14.620
Call me if there's anything.

27:18.710 --> 27:20.180
Isn't that your lady?

27:24.090 --> 27:25.240
She's quite kind,

27:25.280 --> 27:26.340
even coming here.

27:28.760 --> 27:29.950
Are you two on a date

27:29.950 --> 27:30.780
here?

27:31.020 --> 27:31.930
It's inappropriate.

27:32.430 --> 27:33.610
Cut it out.

27:33.960 --> 27:34.570
Let's go.

27:42.870 --> 27:43.910
You're here.

27:44.780 --> 27:46.200
We were classmates after all.

27:46.490 --> 27:47.470
I came to send her off.

27:48.750 --> 27:49.630
Go in.

27:49.660 --> 27:50.850
Her parents are inside.

27:55.150 --> 28:02.840
[Ms. Ding Jing's memorial service]

27:57.320 --> 27:58.270
Thank you.

28:06.040 --> 28:06.860
First bow.

28:08.920 --> 28:10.050
Second bow.

28:12.810 --> 28:13.820
Third bow.

28:15.390 --> 28:16.440
Uncle, Auntie.

28:17.430 --> 28:18.230
My condolences.

28:19.150 --> 28:20.080
Thank you.

28:36.970 --> 28:37.940
First bow.

28:40.240 --> 28:41.370
Second bow.

28:43.720 --> 28:44.750
Third bow.

29:01.270 --> 29:02.120
My condolences.

29:02.510 --> 29:03.360
Thank you.

29:03.930 --> 29:06.470
[Ms. Ding Jing's memorial service]

29:16.550 --> 29:17.540
First bow.

29:17.470 --> 29:18.940
[Ms. Ding Jing's memorial service]

29:52.420 --> 29:53.160
My condolences, Mrs. Ding.

29:53.190 --> 29:53.750
My condolences, Mr. Ding.

29:53.750 --> 29:54.110
Thank you.

29:54.110 --> 29:54.720
Please take care.

29:54.740 --> 29:55.490
Take care of yourselves.

29:58.380 --> 29:59.140
Xiaolin.

29:59.200 --> 29:59.870
Xiaolin!

29:59.910 --> 30:00.390
Mrs. Ding!

30:00.590 --> 30:01.550
-What’s wrong?
-Xiaolin!

30:02.630 --> 30:04.000
Xiaolin! Xiaolin!

30:04.200 --> 30:05.430
Sit first.

30:05.500 --> 30:06.310
-What’s wrong?
-Mrs. Ding.

30:06.330 --> 30:06.950
Are you okay?

30:06.990 --> 30:07.990
W-What's wrong?

30:08.010 --> 30:08.820
What's wrong, Auntie?

30:10.090 --> 30:11.190
I feel weak...

30:12.500 --> 30:13.640
Dizzy...

30:13.670 --> 30:14.960
Is it hypoglycemia?

30:15.000 --> 30:16.670
She's barely eaten these days.

30:17.440 --> 30:18.260
I think

30:18.280 --> 30:20.360
I'll send her home to rest.

30:20.520 --> 30:21.830
Let me take Auntie home.

30:22.710 --> 30:23.900
Thank you.

30:24.200 --> 30:24.830
Here.

30:31.620 --> 30:32.370
Sit here.

30:33.200 --> 30:33.780
Here.

30:35.230 --> 30:36.170
Mrs. Ding.

30:36.420 --> 30:37.660
Are you still sick?

30:40.580 --> 30:41.740
Do you have medicine at home?

30:43.080 --> 30:44.610
The living room upstairs,

30:44.630 --> 30:45.470
in the medicine box.

30:45.470 --> 30:46.510
Okay, I'll get it.

32:06.750 --> 32:07.750
Qin Yue!

32:08.080 --> 32:09.300
The suspect ran towards the funeral.

32:09.360 --> 32:10.270
Stop her.

32:15.000 --> 32:15.880
Lu Yan.

32:15.910 --> 32:17.080
Stay with Auntie.

32:17.100 --> 32:17.890
Don't come out.

32:27.650 --> 32:29.310
Professor Yu, why are you here?

32:29.840 --> 32:30.790
Investigating a case.

32:31.040 --> 32:32.770
You can even investigate here?

32:34.260 --> 32:36.110
Catching the murderer soon

32:37.080 --> 32:39.110
is the best condolence for the deceased,

32:39.320 --> 32:39.870
isn't it?

32:44.320 --> 32:45.350
Don't take what I said that day

32:45.380 --> 32:46.830
personally.

32:46.910 --> 32:48.110
I didn't mean anything else.

32:48.500 --> 32:49.620
I didn't take it to heart.

32:51.760 --> 32:52.870
Stop! Don't run!

32:59.150 --> 32:59.980
What's happening there?

33:00.010 --> 33:00.650
Don't move.

33:00.880 --> 33:01.680
Back off.

33:01.700 --> 33:02.510
Listen to me.

33:02.530 --> 33:02.950
Back off!

33:02.950 --> 33:04.190
It's not too late to put down the knife,

33:04.190 --> 33:05.390
or I'll shoot you dead!

33:05.920 --> 33:06.990
Calm down.

33:07.240 --> 33:08.210
You're surrounded.

33:08.230 --> 33:09.040
You can't run away.

33:09.590 --> 33:10.620
Put down the knife.

33:11.040 --> 33:12.560
There's no need to hurt another person, yeah?

33:14.470 --> 33:15.190
Don't move!

33:16.350 --> 33:17.750
Okay, we'll back off.

33:18.100 --> 33:18.970
Calm down.

33:26.070 --> 33:27.470
We'll back off, okay?

33:27.770 --> 33:28.420
We'll back off.

33:28.460 --> 33:29.270
Calm down.

33:36.100 --> 33:37.350
Don't hurt the hostage!

33:44.990 --> 33:46.170
L-Look at me.

33:46.670 --> 33:48.380
I don't have any weapon.

33:50.140 --> 33:51.550
I'll trade with him, okay?

33:53.060 --> 33:54.610
I'll be the hostage. I'll go with you.
